+
+On Windows, Fix NSIS uninstaller deleting the wrong application data if the delete the application data checkbox is checked.
diff --git a/tooling/bundler/src/bundle/windows/templates/installer.nsi b/tooling/bundler/src/bundle/windows/templates/installer.nsi
index 83f6ce504..356fdcde1 100644
